        <p>śrī-mahāli<lb break="no" n="A12"/>ṅga-devaṁ ke cid atikr̥tya narake patantu<g type="ddandaPlain">.</g> ke cid valātkāreṇāsya dravya-dāsa<milestone n="B" type="pagelike" unit="face"/><lb break="no" n="B1"/>-kṣetra-go-mahiṣān hariṣyanti dahana-śikhā
             <lb n="B2"/>karāle mahāniraye patantu<g type="ddandaPlain">.</g> ye dharmma-jñā nyāyena pāla<lb break="no" n="B3"/>yanti śaktimantam imaṁ te divi vasantu<g type="ddandaPlain">.</g>
           </p>
