             <lb n="D4"/><supplied reason="lost">po</supplied>v· vruv· humā ṅan·
             <lb n="D5"/>nan· Āvista  kā yā<supplied reason="lost">ṅ·</supplied>
             <lb n="D6"/><supplied reason="lost">po</supplied>v· ku śrī jaya Indra<lb break="no" n="D7"/><supplied reason="lost">va</supplied>rmma vuḥ di yāṁ pu po<supplied reason="lost">v·</supplied>
                  </p>
        <lg met="indravajrā" n="8">
